<rs type="material" key="marmor">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType"><rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> shaft</rs>, with moulded panels on all four sides (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.60</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.35</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.54</measure>); broken above, and at the right.  Standing on a plinth.</p>
</div>

